name: FakeValuesService_safeFetchTest
description: Unit tests for the safeFetch method in FakeValuesService.

test_cases.name: testSafeFetchWithNullObject
test_cases.description: Tests the safeFetch method when the key does not exist, ensuring the default value is returned.

test_cases.name: testSafeFetchWithSingleString
test_cases.description: Tests the safeFetch method when the key maps to a single string, ensuring the correct string is returned.

test_cases.name: testSafeFetchWithListOfStrings
test_cases.description: Tests the safeFetch method when the key maps to a list of strings, ensuring one of the strings in the list is returned.

test_cases.name: testSafeFetchWithSlashDelimitedRegex
test_cases.description: Tests the safeFetch method when the key maps to a slash-delimited regex, ensuring the correct formatted string is returned.
